The Three Little pigs left their mothers house to fend themselves. The first Little pig bought straw and used it to build his house. And then a big bad wolf came along and blew the house down and ate the pig. The second little pig built his house with sticks. And then the big bad wolf came along a nd blew the house down and ate the pig. The thrid pig built his house of bricks. And then the big bad wolf came along and tried but did not blow the house down. So he wnet down the fireplace and then fell into the fire and the thrid pig ate him for dinner.